{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_01","textHome":"你好。我是由贵真里爱。放学后作为魔法少女@战斗的同时，也在兼职做着课后托管的姐姐@。虽然也有很辛苦的事情，但是孩子们非常@可爱，工作起来很开心哦。你也来参加一次@试试吗？啊，当然是兼职噢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.6,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_17","textHome":"不能说我想成为保育员的梦想没有受到家庭的@影响。我的父母虽然都是非常优秀的人，但@却没有给我太多的爱…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_18","textHome":"大概除了我家以外，也有很多因为各种各样的@事情而无法对孩子倾注爱意的家庭。如果我@能帮上那些家庭的忙就好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_19","textHome":"那么，快乐的木偶人偶剧要开始啦~"}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_20","textHome":"感觉浑身充满了力量，就是指这种情况吧"}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_21","textHome":"以前对变强什么的没什么兴趣…。但是现在，@我想要变得更强，想要保护更多的孩子们"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_22","textHome":"虽然魔法少女的真相令人吃惊，但我还是想为@了大家能安心生活而战斗。如果魔女能完全@消失的话，我就此消失也无妨。…像这样考@虑的话会被说成是轻率呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_23","textHome":"神滨也好，这场战斗也好…也许状况会越来越@恶化。但是，必须要守护名为未来的希望。@所以，让活在当下的我们展露出笑容吧。不@能让未来充满不安啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_24","textHome":"哎呀，你来了啊。等你好久了。看到你精神饱@满的样子，姐姐我非常开心！那我要点名了@，你要精神饱满的回答哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":1}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_25","textHome":"还很困吗…？嗯…那么！让我来帮你吧！加油@！加油！可以的！可以的！fight！f@ight！…好了，你做得很棒哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_26","textHome":"请将双手合十。…哎呀，我现在不是在打工啊@。但是打招呼还是礼貌点好，继续做完吧。@一—二，我开动了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_02","textHome":"初次见面。我是由贵真里爱。虽然经常被人说@是寡妇或者团地妻，但我还只是个女高中生@而已。…团地妻是什么意思呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_27","textHome":"…哈！这个味道…是哪家在做咖喱吗。活泼的@孩子玩得脏兮兮地回来了…，吃了很多碗饭@…。哼哼，好像很开心呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_28","textHome":"必须要进行下个月的活动中参加的人偶剧的练@习了。…咳嗯。“哎呀哎呀，这可真是美丽@的桃子啊”…老奶奶的声音，模仿得像吗"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_29","textHome":"课后托管要检查活动的琐事和家庭作业。虽然@也有很辛苦的时候，但是我很幸福啊。因为@大家都很可爱啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_30","textHome":"没必要慌张。虽然魔女的反应确实很厉害，但@是有我跟着你。做下深呼吸，等冷静下来之@后就去利落的将魔女打到吧"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_31","textHome":"镜之魔女…真是罪孽深重的魔女啊。就算是伪@造的，和人战斗也会给心理带来很大的负担@。不过，正因如此才更不能逃避…！@@"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_32","textHome":"有这么多魔法少女…！这是，要跟大家战斗吗@…？那样的话就交给姐姐我吧。我已经习惯@了和很多孩子打交道了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_33","textHome":"和孩子们玩的时候要注意一件事。就是放水的@办法。那些孩子们，因为比想象中的要敏感@，所以笨拙的放水的话很快就会暴露了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_34","textHome":"班上的孩子说我是「寡妇」…，但其实别说死@去的丈夫了，我连男朋友都还没有…。有点@寂寞啊…。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_35","textHome":"难道说…是这个卷发让我看起来像是年长的人@吗。嗯，果然很羡慕看上去像是自带天使圆@环的清爽发型啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_36","textHome":"喂！…啊，吓到你了吧。现在是生气的联系。@虽然我不擅长这个，但是我尊敬的老师都很@擅长生气呢…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_03","textHome":"解决了一件事…的话就好了…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_37","textHome":"离开了课后托管的高年级的孩子们偶尔会来玩@。因为有很久没见了，看上去长大了很多啊@，让我有点感动"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400,"tear":1}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_38","textHome":"小萌花虽然有点冒失，但是心底里还是很温柔@的。真希望将这世间变成那样的孩子可以自@由生活的社会啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_39","textHome":"小育梦……很健康也很努力…但是，总觉得有@点消极而且没有自信…。嗯，果然还是放不@下啊"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_40","textHome":"对于成为魔法少女这件事…如果说没有后悔的@话可能是骗人的。但是，如果能减少一点袭@击孩子们的危机的话，那就很让人开心了"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_41","textHome":"哎呀？刚才那个有点太调皮了哦。做错事之后@，该怎么做呢？嗯，能坦率地道歉，了不起@了不起"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":400,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_42","textHome":"这个不太能让孩子们看到呢"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_43","textHome":"那么，准备回去吧"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_44","textHome":"再也不能做这种事了哦"}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_45","textHome":"大家，都做得很棒哦！"}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_46","textHome":"铭记这份痛楚吧"}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_04","textHome":"就算是为了这个孩子…！"}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_05","textHome":"我已经…是魔法少女了啊"}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":1,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_13","textHome":"我想告诉孩子们，脚踏实地地努力的重要性"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_7":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_14","textHome":"原来我也能成长到这种地步啊！…这可不是因@为年龄大哦…？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303600}]}],"group_8":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":200,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_15","textHome":"和孩子们在一起的话，也能感受到他们的父母@的辛苦哦…！"}]}],"group_9":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303600,"motion":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_3036_00_16","textHome":"我将来的梦想是当保育员。事实上，现在除了@在做课后托管的兼职外，偶尔还会去保育园@做下志愿者"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303600,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303600}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303600,"motion":200}]}]},"version":3}